data.description: Contemporary Custom-Built home on cut-de-sac. 0/5 acres with wooded back yard (Protected Patuxent Environmental Area).  Huge deck overlooking Trees and partially Screened. Custom stone patio with beautiful landscaping. Main level Master Bedroom with sitting room, private deck and walk in closet.  Gourmet Kitchen with SS appliances, Granite Counter top, Ceramic Tile Floor, Bar sink, Wine Cooler and Cook Top with downdraft. Large window brings lots of daylight. The upper level has 2nd Family room that easily convert Bedroom if needed. Two Bedroom upstairs, walk in closet and full bath.  The lower level has two bedrooms, huge storage area, full bath, recreation room with wet bar. Jetted Tubs, new smoke detector with carbon monoxide detector.
